ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#245: FILE: arch/x86/kernel/ptrace.c:600:
+	else if ((thbi = alloc_thread_hw_breakpoint(tsk)) == NULL)

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

